title.narrative: Maintaining low HIV prevalence in the Republic of Serbia

description.narrative: Serbia - HIV - Ministry of Health of Republic of Serbia - MOH Serbia. This program has the following goals: To increase the number of diagnosed PLHIV among KP. To strenghten preventive interventions among KP. To improve support to PLHIV. The objectives of this program are: To improve access to VCT services for all 3 KP: MSM, PWID, SW. To implement interventions allowing to increase in KP number of people receiving prevention package of services. To improve partnership between medical facilities and NGOs of PLHIV in order to increase number of PLHIV receiving support especially on adherence issue
